    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Octohill 是一款休闲滑雪度假村模拟游戏，你可以在无数山地地图上尝试建造和管理自己的度假村。你将绘制滑雪道、调整坡地地形，管理财务、交通、建筑和维护，但游戏的核心是精心规划。）</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >从零开始设计你的度假村</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 Octohill 中，你将从零开始建造滑雪度假村。你将选择坡地上的最佳地点，准备地形并标记滑雪道区域，将它们与滑雪缆车和公共道路连接起来，并提供游客所需的一切服务。凭借直观的建筑机制和固定网格布局，你可以放松并专注于规划和创造力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302160/extras/655594b92baeb42e0323b3055d4d6cf3.poster.avif?t=1764025156\" width=800 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302160/extras/655594b92baeb42e0323b3055d4d6cf3.webm?t=1764025156\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302160/extras/655594b92baeb42e0323b3055d4d6cf3.mp4?t=1764025156\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >提升到顶级</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >起初你的度假村吸引的游客很少，但随着你满足他们的需求，你的声誉会逐渐提高，从而让更多的人光顾你的滑雪道，带来更大的收入。每位滑雪者都有自己的偏好和技能，在计划下一次扩展时需要牢记这一点，以确保度假村盈利且游客满意。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302160/extras/9c6c4bdcbc7246e18c4773ab8a5270f7.poster.avif?t=1764025156\" width=800 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302160/extras/9c6c4bdcbc7246e18c4773ab8a5270f7.webm?t=1764025156\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302160/extras/9c6c4bdcbc7246e18c4773ab8a5270f7.mp4?t=1764025156\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >选择你自己的山脉</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Octohill 提供了几个基于真实地点（如法国阿尔卑斯山或落基山脉）的默认地图，你可以用来重现著名的度假村。如果你对这些地图感到厌倦，还可以尝试高度可定制的程序生成地图，甚至加载自己的高度图像。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302160/extras/1ce9ef15140e42317d43dcd4a80b317e.poster.avif?t=1764025156\" width=616 height=173 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302160/extras/1ce9ef15140e42317d43dcd4a80b317e.webm?t=1764025156\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
